{"tid":990794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TRUMP: 中國咪再玩嘢， 浪費時間","createTime":"2019-01-22T01:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T11:29:56.000Z","uid":62257,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"be594bc3d78b275d503ccfe13f07959e61b15b86","tid":990794,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:39:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2257041/【貿易休戰】特朗普促中國「不要胡鬧」%20%20應與美達貿易協議\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2257041%2F%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%BC%91%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E4%BF%83%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%83%A1%E9%AC%A7%E3%80%8D%2520%2520%E6%87%89%E8%88%87%E7%BE%8E%E9%81%94%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0&d=Wqf%2BBtIb0uKZLQ16pRiKQcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b023feb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2257041/【貿易休戰】特朗普促中國「不要胡鬧」%20%20應與美達貿易協議</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2255000/2257041/0122_sc01_600.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2255000%2F2257041%2F0122_sc01_600.PNG&h=fdafb692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地經濟增長放緩，被美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）視為貿易談判中對美方有利的籌碼。昨日國家統計局公布內地去年全年經濟增長6.6%，創28年新低，特朗普即時在推特（twitter）上發帖，促中國為經濟着想，要與美國達成真正的貿易協議，「不要胡鬧」（playing around）。<br />\n美國總統特朗普今晨在推特上發文表示，中國在美國的新政策及貿易磨擦下，去年經濟錄得自1990年以來最慢增速。他稱中國應該與美國達成真正的貿易協議，不要浪費時間。<br />\n<br />\n國家統計局昨公布，去年全年內地GDP按年增速放緩至6.6%，實現了年初設定全年增長6.5%左右的預期發展目標，但為1990年以來的28年新低，且較2017年的6.8%回落0.2個百分點。其中，第四季GDP增速回落至6.4%，為2009年首季以來的近10年季度新低，較對上一季的6.5%輕微回落0.1個百分點。<br />\n中美將於本月底再展經貿磋商，副總理劉鶴應美國財長姆欽（Steven Mnuchin）、貿易代表萊特希澤（Robert Lighthizer）邀請，將於1月30至31日訪美，與美方就兩國經貿問題磋商，共同推動落實兩國元首重要共識。<br />\n本月初中美副部級官員磋商，雙方在中方購買美國商品和服務、中國擴大市場准入等問題上取得進展，但在國企補貼、知識產權等結構性問題上未有進展，預料今次劉鶴赴美談判，要達成協議挑戰仍很大。"},{"pid":"af6fecd09c693aeb73ecd71f734eb05afe7185fd","tid":990794,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:39:58.000Z","msg":"90 日倒數完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400d3dbc06ef6541935a40ddeef051224b6b6a44","tid":990794,"uid":185224,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:40:34.000Z","msg":"靠樓市頂起，個bubble會有幾大。"},{"pid":"ebe51610b4890a06f4a03297f83901c6fc79b88e","tid":990794,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T01:42:55.000Z","msg":"新聞日日話會有好消息 但唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35846e148b808d854a8692252030af34147de155","tid":990794,"uid":27038,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T03:33:22.000Z","msg":"蝗國同你簽撚左都咪撚信丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗一定唔會同你守信用㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a9aaa3fd700976b0daed8241bfb5ce3a80317e","tid":990794,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T05:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1621b15060f0b95f70f3fdb33e16a71dc2881b1c","tid":990794,"uid":124430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"簽咗都可以玩嘢啦 何況未簽 <br />\n簽完伊朗核協議都可以話唔符合利益退出啦<br />\n玩嘢有咩問題先 支持大家攬炒"},{"pid":"09705ef361e671969e900c35dedd246fdd418657","tid":990794,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:02:29.000Z","msg":"人哋就係想浪費時間姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc30c35f85a9df32fac97ed0018147200a9fa3c","tid":990794,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T09:17:10.000Z","msg":"信支那已經fail"},{"pid":"d56a6f9874294971aa7d7efce26bca30340d46f6","tid":990794,"uid":174420,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:35:05.000Z","msg":"侵侵比人撚到發嬲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9071232d289